Heres a glimpse of how lunch/ snack looks in our household. I packed some of the boys favorites of course. I titled it lunch/ snack because I only pack lunch for my oldest son Amir because he goes to school throughout the week. Snack is for Amari because he’s home with me and he only goes to school once out of the week. But I still to go ahead an pack Amari snack so I don’t have to stop whatever I’m doing during the day. So I love using @gobekids snack spinner to store his snacks. It allows him to pick whatever he wants. Recently we visited @kidsempire.us .This indoor playground have so many fun activities and play areas for kids of all ages. Our boys had so much fun even me and hubby had an amazing time. I really like that they have a tots play area separate from the older kids play area. The tots play area was accessible for my little ones to play safely.This really gave me a peace of mind. I will definitely be visiting again because the boys are anxious to go back. So If your in the Johns creek, Ga or Marietta, Ga area I highly recommend that you and your kids visit. If your not in the Ga area no worry’s they have over 50 locations in the U.S. And they are open everyday including holidays. 🤩
